cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.NA, cs.MS 

This paper is about improving the scalability and efficiency of Kernel Ridge Regression (KRR) on parallel and distributed systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also discusses optimization techniques and computational methods, which could fall under cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) and cs.MS (Mathematical Software).
